  "_meta": {
    "description": "Centralized label mappings for Earth Engine land cover datasets",
    "updated": "2026-04-19",
    "comment": "This file contains label mappings, class names, and visualization palettes for various land cover datasets. Palettes harmonized so that recurring concepts (Trees, Grassland, Cropland, Built-up, Water, etc.) share the same canonical color across datasets. Anchored on the ESA WorldCover (UN/FAO LCCS) color scheme, extended with Dynamic World colors for classes WorldCover does not define."
  },
